    <item>
      <title>Projects</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ul class=&#34;project-list&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;li class=&#34;project-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/0yukali0/ResourceUsageReporter&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;ResourceUsageReporter&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Bridges the gap of real-time node metrics in Kubernetes, enabling schedulers to make more informed placement decisions.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Kubernetes&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Go&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Metrics&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;li class=&#34;project-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/0yukali0/my-skills&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;My-skills&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Implements agent-invocable skills that submit workflows directly to Kubernetes, enabling Claude and local LLMs to trigger jobs such as web search and model training, ray training.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Kubernetes&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Claude&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;LLM&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Ray&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;MLOps&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;li class=&#34;project-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-name&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/0yukali0/postgres-metrics-observability&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Postgres-metrics-observability&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-desc&#34;&gt;Collects Postgres metrics via OpenTelemetry Collector and visualizes DB usage and latency in Grafana, enabling data-driven query tuning and alert configuration.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-tags&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Postgres&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;OpenTelemetry&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Grafana&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;tag&#34;&gt;Observability&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA;.project-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }&#xA;.project-item { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 1rem; }&#xA;.project-name { font-size: 1.1em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }&#xA;.project-desc { color: #555; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }&#xA;.project-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }&#xA;.tag { background: #f0f0f0; color: #333; padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.8em; }&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Resume</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/resume/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/resume/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Apache Yunikorn &lt;strong&gt;PMC Member&lt;/strong&gt; and Software Engineer with 1+ years at &lt;strong&gt;ASUS&lt;/strong&gt;. Merged &lt;strong&gt;31+ PRs (75 commits)&lt;/strong&gt; across Apache Yunikorn and Flyte; led the &lt;strong&gt;v1.3.0 release&lt;/strong&gt; and benchmarked scheduling throughput at &lt;strong&gt;204 pods/sec on 2K nodes&lt;/strong&gt; (4.2× faster than default scheduler). Core expertise: &lt;strong&gt;Kubernetes observability&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;MLOps&lt;/strong&gt; (Flyte, Ray), &lt;strong&gt;GPU monitoring&lt;/strong&gt;, distributed tracing (OpenTelemetry), and cloud-native backend development in Go &amp;amp; Python.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;technical-skills&#34;&gt;Technical Skills&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harness Engineering:&lt;/strong&gt; Copilot, Antigravity, Claude Code, Openspec, Hook, Skill, MCP&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
